<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{#if lang}}{{lang}}{{else}}fr{{/if}}">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>{{#eq lang "en"}}FASO DIGITALISATION — Activate your administrator account{{else}}FASO DIGITALISATION — Activez votre compte administrateur{{/eq}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f3f6f4;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f6f4;padding:32px 0;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table width="640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;padding:28px 32px;">
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;">FASO DIGITALISATION</h1>
            <p style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#FFD700;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Administrator onboarding — magic link{{else}}Activation administrateur — lien magique{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px;color:#222;">
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Hello,{{else}}Bonjour,{{/eq}}
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}<strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to join the FASO administration console as <strong>{{targetRole}}</strong>. Click the secure button below to validate ownership of this email and proceed to MFA enrolment (PassKey + TOTP + recovery codes).{{else}}<strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> vous invite à rejoindre la console d'administration FASO en tant que <strong>{{targetRole}}</strong>. Cliquez sur le bouton ci-dessous pour valider la propriété de cet e-mail puis configurer vos facteurs MFA (PassKey + TOTP + codes de récupération).{{/eq}}
            </p>

            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:28px 0;">
              <tr><td align="center">
                <a href="{{magicLink}}" style="display:inline-block;background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:6px;border:2px solid #1b5e20;">
                  {{#eq lang "en"}}Activate my administrator account{{else}}Activer mon compte administrateur{{/eq}}
                </a>
              </td></tr>
            </table>

            <p style="font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}If the button does not work, copy this URL into your browser:{{else}}Si le bouton ne fonctionne pas, copiez cette URL dans votre navigateur :{{/eq}}<br/>
              <span style="font-family:monospace;color:#1b5e20;word-break:break-all;">{{magicLink}}</span>
            </p>

            <table width="100%" style="margin:28px 0 12px;border-collapse:collapse;background:#f9f9f9;border-radius:6px;">
              <tr><td style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:12px;color:#666;width:35%;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Inviter{{else}}Invité par{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;">{{inviterName}}</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:12px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Inviter source IP{{else}}IP de l'inviteur{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;font-family:monospace;">{{ipAddress}}</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Link valid for{{else}}Lien valable{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;"><strong>{{expiresInMinutes}}</strong> {{#eq lang "en"}}minutes — single-use{{else}}minutes — usage unique{{/eq}}</td></tr>
            </table>

            <div style="background:#fbf3d8;border:2px solid #1b5e20;border-radius:8px;padding:18px 22px;margin-top:24px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#1b5e20;line-height:1.5;">
                <strong>{{#eq lang "en"}}Security advice{{else}}Conseil sécurité{{/eq}}</strong> &mdash;
                {{#eq lang "en"}}This link is single-use and expires in {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes. Before clicking, verify the URL begins with <strong>https://admin.faso.bf</strong>. After clicking, the page will display an 8-digit code to enter <em>on the same browser tab</em> — never share that code, even with FASO support.{{else}}Ce lien est à usage unique et expire dans {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes. Avant de cliquer, vérifiez que l'URL commence bien par <strong>https://admin.faso.bf</strong>. Après le clic, la page affichera un code à 8 chiffres à saisir <em>sur le même onglet</em> — ne partagez jamais ce code, même avec le support FASO.{{/eq}}
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background:#fff3e0;border:2px solid #E53935;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 18px;margin-top:18px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:12.5px;color:#b71c1c;line-height:1.5;">
                <strong>{{#eq lang "en"}}Did not request this?{{else}}Vous n'attendiez pas cette invitation ?{{/eq}}</strong>
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Ignore this email and report it to <a href="mailto:security@faso.bf" style="color:#b71c1c;">security@faso.bf</a>.{{else}}Ignorez cet e-mail et signalez-le à <a href="mailto:security@faso.bf" style="color:#b71c1c;">security@faso.bf</a>.{{/eq}}
              </p>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#FFD700;padding:14px 32px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
            FASO DIGITALISATION — République du Burkina Faso<br/>
            <a href="https://faso.bf/security" style="color:#FFD700;text-decoration:underline;">https://faso.bf/security</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
